Package com.franz.agraph.repository.config

Repository creation and configuration for AllegroGraph.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
AGRepositoryConfig Configuration for an AllegroGraph Repository.
AGRepositoryFactory A RepositoryFactory that creates AGRepositorys based on RDF configuration data.
AGRepositorySchema Defines constants for the AGRepository schema which is used by AGRepositoryFactorys to initialize AGRepositorys.
